node.title: Evidence in the Barbara Kendhammer case
node.description: Does the evidence show a cover-up, or was Todd Kendhammer wrongfully convicted for the murder of his wife?
node.content: ["Does the evidence show a cover-up, or was Todd Kendhammer wrongfully convicted for the murder of his wife? \"48 Hours\" investigates in \"Mystery on County Road M.\"", "On\u00a0                 the morning of September 16, 2016, Todd Kendhammer called 911 reporting he and his wife, Barbara, had been in a car accident on a rural road near La Crosse, Wisconsin. \u00a0", "During the call, a distraught Todd told the operator he believed Barbara was \"\u2026 hit in the head and in the throat,\" and when authorities arrived, Todd said the car was struck by a pipe that came off a truck.", "Barbara was rushed to the hospital. Unable to survive her injuries, she passed away the next morning."]
